                <h4></h4>

    
              <p>3 credits, one of:</p>
    
              <ul class="program-set">
                  <li class="program-course">
            <a href="/study/2014-2015/courses/chem-203" class="program-course-title">
              CHEM 203 Survey of Physical Chemistry (3 credits)              <!---->            </a>
            <div class="program-course-description">
              <div class="program-course-description-inner">
                <div id="node-20348" class=" clearfix">
  
  
  
  <div class="meta">
    <p>Offered by: Chemistry (<a href="/study/2014-2015/node/615">Faculty of Science</a>)</p>
      </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Chemistry              : The fundamentals of thermodynamics and chemical kinetics with applications to biomolecular systems. Thermodynamic and kinetic control of biological processes.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
      Terms:              Fall 2014          </p>

