              <li>Winter</li>
              <li>2 lectures each week</li>
              <li>Prerequisites or Corequisites: BIOL 201, or PHGY 209, or PHGY 210; and one of ANAT 321, ANAT 322, BIOL 306, PHGY 311.</li>
            </ul>
      </div>

  </div> <!-- /.node -->
